column5: I went to bayfront park today to cast for some pike, ended up getting this guy.      bassmaster4
Nice, finally a picture of someone with a pike from the harbour.What did you catch it on?
I'd be interested as well,that water looks clear.Let us know what your using early this season
Nice fish, WTG champ! It also looks nice and mild out your way.
Good deal and a nice fish.   Art
Thanks guys! I got it on a silver and blue x-rap.
Good job there Bassmaster4.  A lot of guys have been coming up empty casting for gators.  Nice!
Nice shooting  I was tempted to cast a line, but I was too sick to bother. Just out for some fresh air.
That's a nice one. And thanks for sharing your picture.
nice. i tried for 3 hours with live minnows and not even a bite.
when did you try? I was there today and got skunked, I think the rain and cooler temperature probably had something to do with it.
sunday... it was a beautiful day I dont understand why I dident catch anything, usaully something is biting at bayfront
